column5: i just went out again today for an hour, got skunked again.  Ice was a good 8-10 inches.  What am i doing wrong? i should be atleast getting perch.

Definitely thicker than it looks ! If you see some guy wandering around wondering where the hell his hut went... tell him it's smashed against the dock over at the dock lunch ! Blew all the way across the bay.
wow, it was definatly windy enough though, power was out for like 14 hours the other day. Im surprised our shed in a box, and the garage in a box stayed put.
Were you fishing over in front of Hindson or up in the North West Basin?
i was in the cluster of huts.  There were a couple of guys at the point by the Basin though.
hey bro im in barrie..never ished that way....im fishing little lake in barrie right now..i would love to get out to penetang...what are you supposed to be catching where you are????
pike and perch, i caught a largie once.  and i think Cisco?? may come around sometimes.
